N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 2620.7 - Technical assistance

State Regulations
(a) The
division may render to qualified applicants such technical services and
assistance to enable such applicants to comply with the intent and purposes of
these rules and regulations. (b) The division may contract with municipal and other public agencies and with
private persons, firms and corporations for the rendering of technical services
and assistance to qualified applicants. Notes
